===Verb===
[[Category:Japanese Type 2 Verbs]]
'''いる''' (''iru'')

The kanji form of いる is 居る, but the term is usually written in [[hiragana]] (i.e. as いる).
# (''of animate objects'') to [[exist]], to [[be]]
# (''of animate objects'') to [[have]]
#: [[有る]] ([[ある]], ''aru'') is the equivalent term used with inanimate objects.
# ''(preceded by a ''て''-form verb)'' to be (doing)

